# placeholder — record locally and overwrite
# regenerate via `make demo`
#
# This file is intentionally empty. To produce a real recording:
#
#   1. Build the binary so the demo script can find it:
#        go build -o thimble ./cmd/thimble
#   2. Record:
#        asciinema rec assets/demo.cast bash scripts/demo.sh
#   3. Commit the recording.
#
# A real .cast is a JSON-Lines stream beginning with a header object
# (asciicast v2). Asciinema overwrites this comment on first record.
